<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">定身减除法，定被除数首位为首商，从被除数次位起减去首商乘除数次位及以后各数的积，再定余数首位为次商，从余数次位起减去次商乘除数次位及以后各数的积，如此继续求三商、四商，直至除尽，或除至要求位数的商数。方法一，适合于除数首位为“1”，次位为“0”或“1”、“2”等小数字。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">14260÷115=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">14260÷115</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=(14200+60)÷115</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=100+2760÷115</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=100+20+460÷115</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=120+4</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=124</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>